{"tid":1689826,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"純討論 黑警會唔會啪左藥?","createTime":"2019-11-03T04:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T05:11:23.000Z","uid":317805,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3ba0c2726dc099b608763d2fc5d65e46c2a590e3","tid":1689826,"uid":317805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:19:51.000Z","msg":"我有個醫生朋友做精神科<br />\n佢話呢排d黑警癲到好似啪左藥咁<br />\n<br />\n我即刻番去search下<br />\n原來<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">納粹德軍同日軍</span></span>以前都有咁嘅做法<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">麻黃鹼（ephedrine)</span>，實驗證實這類物質可以興奮交感神經、抑制自律神經。<br />\n軍人服用脫氧麻黃鹼後變得不知疲倦、勇猛異常，而且情緒高漲、鬥志旺盛，最神祕的是駕駛技能完全不受影響，精細操作似乎更加嫻熟。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">安非他命</span>是一種神經中樞興奮藥，服用後會明顯感覺自信心倍增，變得膽大冒險又精神高度集中，容易亢奮激動。與此同時，饑餓、口渴、疼痛等感覺會減弱，甚至不想睡覺。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/138665/%E4%BA%8C%E6%88%B0%E5%BE%B7%E8%BB%8D-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A5%9E%E9%A2%A8%E6%95%A2%E6%AD%BB%E9%9A%8A%E5%A6%82%E6%AD%A4%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82-%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E9%9D%A0%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E4%BB%A4%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E4%BA%A2%E5%A5%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F138665%2F%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E8%25BB%258D-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%25A5%259E%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%2595%25A2%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%25AD%25A4%25E7%2598%258B%25E7%258B%2582-%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E9%259D%25A0%25E7%25A7%2598%25E5%25AF%2586%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E4%25BA%25A2%25E5%25A5%25AE&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpJODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=0115238f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/138665/%E4%BA%8C%E6%88%B0%E5%BE%B7%E8%BB%8D-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A5%9E%E9%A2%A8%E6%95%A2%E6%AD%BB%E9%9A%8A%E5%A6%82%E6%AD%A4%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82-%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E9%9D%A0%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E4%BB%A4%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E4%BA%A2%E5%A5%AE</a></span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得黑警最近嘅表現實在太癲 <br />\n特別係情緒失晒控 <br />\n如果黑警真係啪左藥 甚至係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毒品</span></span><br />\n份量相信只會越食越多<br />\n而且會有嚴重副作用<br />\n好快就會比人發現<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">集思廣益 <br />\n有咩對應策略撚狗?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">本人生性樂觀 並無自殺傾向 絕不自殺</span>"},{"pid":"6fe43f093b1e3065dd868df6d084eb7d56a230f5","tid":1689826,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:20:42.000Z","msg":"自爆中煙果班企係啲煙上面都無野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51758b0bc3b394089c9908b888a9e46d292f388","tid":1689826,"uid":317805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"推唔郁呀我!"},{"pid":"a4fdb302e3e436ac44fe0ed4f2d5a69e6c1411c6","tid":1689826,"uid":317805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:24:08.000Z","msg":"推唔郁呀屌!"},{"pid":"7202759619b4cf8e235ccca7fcc16e81bf89f015","tid":1689826,"uid":203332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"941330483f4d3cbc3c9e33ec55f94f5bec679d05","tid":1689826,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"幾個月前已經有人出過post啦"},{"pid":"2cee098f45f510cddc9c39600533a1b62f2a8165","tid":1689826,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"可能啪咗都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169db987622fd18c29c687b01d9b26cd3349ce4f","tid":1689826,"uid":104965,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:28:49.000Z","msg":"癲狗一定有食藥<br />\n<br />\n有時候 抗爭手足激